body:
### Welcome to BigOz on GitHub
All of my projects are listed, starting with the most recent.

[reversi_ai_testbed](https://github.com/BigOz/reversi_ai_testbed)
A platform for testing the performance of various AI agents in the game of Reversi. Includes a human agent, random agent, and monte-carlo agent.

[checkers_ai_testbed](https://github.com/BigOz/checkers_ai_testbed)
A platform for testing the performance of various AI agents in the game of Reversi. Includes a human agent, random agent, monte-carlo agent, and alpha-beta pruning agent.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
